Name: Book
Description: A well known novel written by a very renowned writer... not sure who could it be.
es_Description: Una novela muy conocida escrita por un autor muy aclamado por la critica... no se quien sea.

Name: Bookshelf
Description: A wooden board and a couple of nails of dubious quality. I wouldn't place a whole book saga on it.
es_Description: Una tabla y un par de clavos de dudosa calidad. No podría una saga completa de libros sobre ella.

Name: Camera
Description: With the almost latest technology, this camera can be place anywhere inside (not suitable for exteriors)
es_Description: Con tecnología de anteultima, esta camara puede colocarse en cualquier interior (No apta para exteriores).

Name: Chair
Description: At the store you've found the most comfy chair in the world. With unique materials. It was way too expensive.
es_Description: En la tienda viste la silla mas comoda que jamas existio. Con materiales unicos. Era cara y compraste esta.

Name: Chess Board
Description: A perfect board to play chess. Or checkers. Or curling... it is true, google it.
es_Description: Un tablero perfecto para jugar al ajedrez. O a las damas. O al curling... es verdad, googlealo.

Name: ChoppingBoard
Description: The board was in discount because the previous owner chopped his finger off with it. It's still bloody.
es_Description: La tabla estaba en descuento porque el anterior dueño se rebano el dedo con ella. Aun tiene sangre.

Name: Coconut
Description: If we delete it from the game, it won't compile.
es_Description: Si lo borramos del juego, no compila.

Name: Strange Cube
Description: In the event that the strange Cube does speak, F.a.r team urges you to disregard its advice.
es_Description: En el caso de que el Cubo Raro hable, F.a.r team te insta a ignorar su consejo.

Name: Computer
Description: A computer that has KTA preinstalled.
es_Description: Una computadora que viene con KTA preinstalado.

Name: Console
Description: A cubic console with a huge green X and the first CD reader in history.
es_Description: Una consola de juegos con forma cubica, una equis verde enorme y el primer lector de CDs de la historia.

Name: Counter
Description: This outlined square seems to be a counter. Such disastrous artists.
es_Description: Este cuadrado delineado parece ser una mesada. Que artistas nefastos.

Name: Desk
Description: 8 out of 10 people misplaces this desk.
es_Description: 8 de cada 10 personas colocan mal este escritorio.

Name: Dishes
Description: Stacking dishes in pixel art is very complicated, do not complain.
es_Description: Apilar platos en pixel art es muy complicado, no se quejen.

Name: Dumbbells
Description: This dumbbell set ranks from 200g to 4T.
es_Description: Este set de pesas va desde 200g a 4T.

Name: Fridge
Description: Inside there are two bee eggs, an expired milk carton and a vegetable you don't remember buying.
es_Description: Adentro hay dos huevos de abeja, un carton de leche vencida y una verdura que no recuerdas haber comprado.

Name: Pipeline Kit
Description: Use it to connect objects to the water supply.
es_Description: Sirve para conectar objetos a la red de agua.
